Mileter/edit
Editing files with C++ and Curses.

CONTRIBUTING
To contribute, one needs the follow this agreement.

1.  After you are done editing files, before they can be merged, contributers'
    must run tools/indent_all.sh or tools/indent_all_wo.sh, unmodified.
2.  Any changes to these the tools directory, such as adding tools, removing
    tools, and changing tools, must be tested, and deemed to fit the source.
	Only if these changes are accepted, can they be merged.
3.  There should be no obvious issues when compiling, and rigouriously testing
    the contributed program. 